Option 1 (Tried):
  Drag an image
  Choose a transparent shape
  Insert the URL to 'URL Opened When Image Is Clicked'
  Make it 'Floating'
  Cover the text with the image
  Edit the text to look like hyperlink
  
  Option 2 (Web Edit): 
    Select the text
    Press CTRL+V
    Text turns to a hyperlink
    Edit the URL by selecting the text
    
   5 Things You Can Do in Web Edit, But NOT Tableau Desktop: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dU4y_HILCtE
